explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the trends and risk factors of third- and fourth-degree perineal tears among primiparous women in England. It uses a retrospective cohort study design and multivariable logistic regression for analysis. None of the provided keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or other computational methods are mentioned or implied in the title or abstract. The study is purely epidemiological and clinical in nature, without any application of the listed computational techniques.
